    "description": "SISYPHE 是一款冒险游戏，讲述了一个渴望变成圆形的正方形的故事。你要在旅途中的某些地方削去正方形的碎片，然后爬上一座山，寻找新生。在攀登山路的途中，您将经过七个视觉上截然不同的区域。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>SISYPHE 主要是一款互动艺术作品。它是一款精美的休闲攀爬游戏，注重氛围和体验。 SISYPHE 保持了独特的视觉风格，体现了广场之旅的感觉和灵魂。沿途还可聆听由 Pierre Scheuer（PeterBarn）和 Lucas Ljunggren 制作的优美配乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=692 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索一个充满攀岩可能性的绚丽世界。没有无形的墙壁，没有任何限制，在任何地方都可以攀爬。沿途还能发现大型文物和雕像，是领略大自然风光的好去处。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/2510d7609405e8bdec509642a60603c8.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=656 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/2510d7609405e8bdec509642a60603c8.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/2510d7609405e8bdec509642a60603c8.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索《SISYPHE》，这是一款关于 “方变圆 ”的精美休闲攀岩游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/411e3bc0d065fdfcd96598719629dff6.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=696 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/411e3bc0d065fdfcd96598719629dff6.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/411e3bc0d065fdfcd96598719629dff6.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
